texts.base_content: 庆历四年春，滕子京谪守巴陵郡。
texts.content: {"text": "庆历四年春，滕子京谪守巴陵郡。", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 15]}]}

texts.base_content: 越明年，政通人和，百废具兴，乃重修岳阳楼，增其旧制，刻唐贤今人诗赋于其上，属予作文以记之。
texts.content: {"text": "越明年，政通人和，百废具兴，乃重修岳阳楼，增其旧制，刻唐贤今人诗赋于其上，属予作文以记之。", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 45]}]}

texts.base_content: (具 通：俱)　　予观夫巴陵胜状，在洞庭一湖。
texts.content: {"text": "(具 通：俱)　　予观夫巴陵胜状，在洞庭一湖。", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 23]}]}

texts.base_content: 衔远山，吞长江，浩浩汤汤，横无际涯，朝晖夕阴，气象万千，此则岳阳楼之大观也，前人之述备矣。
texts.content: {"text": "衔远山，吞长江，浩浩汤汤，横无际涯，朝晖夕阴，气象万千，此则岳阳楼之大观也，前人之述备矣。", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 45]}]}

texts.base_content: 然则北通巫峡，南极潇湘，迁客骚人，多会于此，览物之情，得无异乎？
texts.content: {"text": "然则北通巫峡，南极潇湘，迁客骚人，多会于此，览物之情，得无异乎？", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 32]}]}

texts.base_content: 若夫淫雨霏霏，连月不开，阴风怒号，浊浪排空，日星隐曜，山岳潜形，商旅不行，樯倾楫摧，薄暮冥冥，虎啸猿啼。
texts.content: {"text": "若夫淫雨霏霏，连月不开，阴风怒号，浊浪排空，日星隐曜，山岳潜形，商旅不行，樯倾楫摧，薄暮冥冥，虎啸猿啼。", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 52]}]}

texts.base_content: 登斯楼也，则有去国怀乡，忧谗畏讥，满目萧然，感极而悲者矣。
texts.content: {"text": "登斯楼也，则有去国怀乡，忧谗畏讥，满目萧然，感极而悲者矣。", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 29]}]}

texts.base_content: (隐曜 一作：隐耀；
texts.content: {"text": "(隐曜 一作：隐耀；", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 10]}]}

texts.base_content: 淫雨 通：霪雨)　　至若春和景明，波澜不惊，上下天光，一碧万顷，沙鸥翔集，锦鳞游泳，岸芷汀兰，郁郁青青。
texts.content: {"text": "淫雨 通：霪雨)　　至若春和景明，波澜不惊，上下天光，一碧万顷，沙鸥翔集，锦鳞游泳，岸芷汀兰，郁郁青青。", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 52]}]}

texts.base_content: 而或长烟一空，皓月千里，浮光跃金，静影沉璧，渔歌互答，此乐何极！
texts.content: {"text": "而或长烟一空，皓月千里，浮光跃金，静影沉璧，渔歌互答，此乐何极！", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 32]}]}

texts.base_content: 登斯楼也，则有心旷神怡，宠辱偕忘，把酒临风，其喜洋洋者矣。
texts.content: {"text": "登斯楼也，则有心旷神怡，宠辱偕忘，把酒临风，其喜洋洋者矣。", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 29]}]}

texts.base_content: 嗟夫！
texts.content: {"text": "嗟夫！", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 3]}]}

texts.base_content: 予尝求古仁人之心，或异二者之为，何哉？
texts.content: {"text": "予尝求古仁人之心，或异二者之为，何哉？", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 19]}]}

texts.base_content: 不以物喜，不以己悲，居庙堂之高则忧其民，处江湖之远则忧其君。
texts.content: {"text": "不以物喜，不以己悲，居庙堂之高则忧其民，处江湖之远则忧其君。", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 30]}]}

texts.base_content: 是进亦忧，退亦忧。
texts.content: {"text": "是进亦忧，退亦忧。", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 9]}]}

texts.base_content: 然则何时而乐耶？
texts.content: {"text": "然则何时而乐耶？", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 8]}]}

texts.base_content: 其必曰：“先天下之忧而忧，后天下之乐而乐”乎！
texts.content: {"text": "其必曰：“先天下之忧而忧，后天下之乐而乐”乎！", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 23]}]}

texts.base_content: 噫！
texts.content: {"text": "噫！", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 2]}]}

texts.base_content: 微斯人，吾谁与归？
texts.content: {"text": "微斯人，吾谁与归？", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 9]}]}

texts.base_content: 时六年九月十五日。
texts.content: {"text": "时六年九月十五日。", "styles": [{"size": 6, "font": {"path": "C:/Users/Administrator/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.9.0.11632/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf", "id": ""}, "fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.13, 0.63, 0.24]}}}, "range": [0, 9]}]}
